"title": "7552: Pharisees, attitudes to Jesus Christ",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7552: pharisees, attitudes to jesus christ",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Pharisees opposed Jesus Christ during his ministry and were among those who brought about his crucifixion. Some Pharisees, however, accepted Christ's teaching and believed in him.</p>\n<h2>Dialogue between Jesus Christ and Pharisees</h2>\n<h3>They demanded a sign to prove his messiahship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:38-Matt12:42\">MAT 12:38–12:42</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:29-Luke11:32\">LUK 11:29–11:32</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:1-Matt16:4\">MAT 16:1–16:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:11-Mark8:12\">MRK 8:11–8:12</a></p>\n<h3>They questioned him on matters of the law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:3-Matt19:9\">MAT 19:3–19:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:2-Mark10:9\">MRK 10:2–10:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:15-Matt22:22\">MAT 22:15–22:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:13-Mark12:17\">MRK 12:13–12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:20-Luke20:26\">LUK 20:20–20:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:34-Matt22:40\">MAT 22:34–22:40</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:28-Mark12:34\">MRK 12:28–12:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:3-John8:11\">JHN 8:3–8:11</a></p>\n<h3>They called him Teacher</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:13-Mark12:14\">MRK 12:13–12:14</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:15-Matt22:16\">MAT 22:15–22:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:38\">MAT 12:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:34-Matt22:36\">MAT 22:34–22:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:39-Luke7:40\">LUK 7:39–7:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:39\">LUK 19:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:21\">LUK 20:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:28\">LUK 20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:2\">JHN 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:3-John8:4\">JHN 8:3–8:4</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ questioned them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:41-Matt22:46\">MAT 22:41–22:46</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:35-Mark12:40\">MRK 12:35–12:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:41-Luke20:44\">LUK 20:41–20:44</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:9-Matt12:14\">MAT 12:9–12:14</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:1-Mark3:6\">MRK 3:1–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:6-Luke6:11\">LUK 6:6–6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:24-Matt21:27\">MAT 21:24–21:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:29-Mark11:33\">MRK 11:29–11:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:3-Luke20:8\">LUK 20:3–20:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:1-Luke14:6\">LUK 14:1–14:6</a></p>\n<h2>Social contact between Jesus Christ and Pharisees</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:36\">LUK 7:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:1-Mark7:2\">MRK 7:1–7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:37\">LUK 11:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:31\">LUK 13:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:1\">LUK 14:1</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ criticised the Pharisees</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:1\">LUK 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:20\">MAT 5:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:5-Matt16:12\">MAT 16:5–16:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:14-Mark8:21\">MRK 8:14–8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:33-Matt21:45\">MAT 21:33–21:45</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:1-Mark12:11\">MRK 12:1–12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:9-Luke20:19\">LUK 20:9–20:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:1-Matt23:36\">MAT 23:1–23:36</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:38-Mark12:40\">MRK 12:38–12:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:45-Luke20:47\">LUK 20:45–20:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:37-Luke11:52\">LUK 11:37–11:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:1-Luke16:15\">LUK 16:1–16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a></p>\n<h2>The Pharisees opposed Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:53-Luke11:54\">LUK 11:53–11:54</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2-Matt9:7\">MAT 9:2–9:7</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:3-Mark2:12\">MRK 2:3–2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:17-Luke5:26\">LUK 5:17–5:26</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:10-Matt9:13\">MAT 9:10–9:13</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:15-Mark2:17\">MRK 2:15–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:29-Luke5:32\">LUK 5:29–5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:32-Matt9:34\">MAT 9:32–9:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22-Matt12:24\">MAT 12:22–12:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:22\">MRK 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:1-Matt12:2\">MAT 12:1–12:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:23-Mark2:24\">MRK 2:23–2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:1-Luke6:2\">LUK 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:9-Matt12:14\">MAT 12:9–12:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:1-Mark3:6\">MRK 3:1–3:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:7\">LUK 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:1-Luke14:6\">LUK 14:1–14:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:13-John9:16\">JHN 9:13–9:16</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:36-Luke7:39\">LUK 7:36–7:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:1-Luke15:2\">LUK 15:1–15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:37-Luke19:40\">LUK 19:37–19:40</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:13\">JHN 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:39-John9:41\">JHN 9:39–9:41</a></p>\n<h2>The Pharisees were among those who engineered Jesus Christ's death</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:6\">MRK 3:6</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:14\">MAT 12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:11\">LUK 6:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:45-Matt21:46\">MAT 21:45–21:46</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:12\">MRK 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:19\">LUK 20:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:13\">MRK 12:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:20\">LUK 20:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:62-Matt27:64\">MAT 27:62–27:64</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:32-John7:49\">JHN 7:32–7:49</a></p>\n<h2>Some Pharisees believed in Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:4-Phil3:11\">PHP 3:4–3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:1-John3:2\">JHN 3:1–3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:42\">JHN 12:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:38-John19:40\">JHN 19:38–19:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:5\">ACT 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:6-Acts23:9\">ACT 23:6–23:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:5\">ACT 26:5</a></p>",
